    <note type="biography">
        <p>Mother of Gould Anne Wolfe. Daughter of James Carlyle of Craddockstown, county Kildare. Married Henry Upton Ruxton RN (d. 1826), second son of William Ruxton of Ardee House, county Louth, in 1814. Married in 1829, in Florence, John Henry Offley. Lived in Dublin from 1866 until her death.</p></note>
